                        <interp inst="t18510512-1219-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">of receiving, and witness the juries<lb></lb>diction of this Court.</hi>
